Transmitter data push summary: Assessing the effects of aquaculture operations on the distribution and abundance of pelagic fishes and large predators in the Bay of Fundy. ##### Évaluation des effets des opérations aquaculture sur la distribution et l’abondance des poissons pélagiques et des grands prédateurs dans la baie de Fundy.

Author

Created with the otndo R package (v. 0.1.2)

These are data related to matched transmitter data from the June 2023 OTN data push. New matched-to-animal files (“matched” files) were uploaded on June 15. The previous data push occurred on March 16, 2023.

Overall

A total of 43,696 detections of 55 individuals have been matched via ACT, FACT, and/or OTN. The detections span across 8 different projects consisting of 12 principal investigators.
